PLEASE DO NOT TRY TO INCREASE THE CUSTOM LOCATION ARRAY SIZE!
TOO MANY LOCATIONS WILL BOG DOWN THE SCRIPT!
21 CUSTOM LOCATIONS SHOULD BE PLENTY!
